<HEADLINE> Vikings Sign Tyrone Carter  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDEN PRAIRIE, Minn. (AP) -- The Minnesota Vikings on Friday
agreed to contract terms with All-America safety Tyrone Carter and
Mike Malano.
</P>
